  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An unchanging, deceptive full moon looms over Tokyo, </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>where peaceful nights are now lost to the zombies...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIGH-SPEED SURVIVAL ACTION WITH JUST 2 BUTTONS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/f697a37f193c10f69184e728916a76e4.poster.avif?t=1732546860\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/f697a37f193c10f69184e728916a76e4.webm?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/f697a37f193c10f69184e728916a76e4.mp4?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple Controls, Thrilling Combat</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stand your ground and slash zombies attacking from both sides!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the game with just two buttons, or play comfortably with mouse clicks, keyboard, or gamepad</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chain your attacks to increase damage and score - but beware, enemies will speed up too! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/d59ded66e95e443309b6c4238268fe6d.poster.avif?t=1732546860\" width=798 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/d59ded66e95e443309b6c4238268fe6d.webm?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/d59ded66e95e443309b6c4238268fe6d.mp4?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock & Power Up</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Power up your character with collected coins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your fighting style with 15 different upgrades, including 3 devastating flame techniques</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself with high scores and time attack modes! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/402ff0407384e6daa38b47382bb47be5.poster.avif?t=1732546860\" width=800 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/402ff0407384e6daa38b47382bb47be5.webm?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/402ff0407384e6daa38b47382bb47be5.mp4?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since the unchanging, deceptive full moon began to rise, this city has lost its peaceful nights. In the zombie-infested streets of nighttime Tokyo, where people wander under the moon's spell, \"Hibana\" stands her ground against the hordes of zombies. As a member of NEF (Nyx Eradication Foundation), she fights to reclaim the waning moon she glimpsed in her youth.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An unchanging, deceptive full moon looms over Tokyo, </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>where peaceful nights are now lost to the zombies...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIGH-SPEED SURVIVAL ACTION WITH JUST 2 BUTTONS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/f697a37f193c10f69184e728916a76e4.poster.avif?t=1732546860\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/f697a37f193c10f69184e728916a76e4.webm?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/f697a37f193c10f69184e728916a76e4.mp4?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple Controls, Thrilling Combat</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stand your ground and slash zombies attacking from both sides!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the game with just two buttons, or play comfortably with mouse clicks, keyboard, or gamepad</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chain your attacks to increase damage and score - but beware, enemies will speed up too! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/d59ded66e95e443309b6c4238268fe6d.poster.avif?t=1732546860\" width=798 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/d59ded66e95e443309b6c4238268fe6d.webm?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/d59ded66e95e443309b6c4238268fe6d.mp4?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock & Power Up</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Power up your character with collected coins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your fighting style with 15 different upgrades, including 3 devastating flame techniques</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself with high scores and time attack modes! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/402ff0407384e6daa38b47382bb47be5.poster.avif?t=1732546860\" width=800 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/402ff0407384e6daa38b47382bb47be5.webm?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295300/extras/402ff0407384e6daa38b47382bb47be5.mp4?t=1732546860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since the unchanging, deceptive full moon began to rise, this city has lost its peaceful nights. In the zombie-infested streets of nighttime Tokyo, where people wander under the moon's spell, \"Hibana\" stands her ground against the hordes of zombies. As a member of NEF (Nyx Eradication Foundation), she fights to reclaim the waning moon she glimpsed in her youth.</p>",
